Viki-Wiki demo corpus — attribution and license
================================================

The file demo_corpora/viki_wiki.zip contains 200 pairs of French texts
(viki_*.txt / wiki_*.txt). Each pair is the same encyclopedic topic at two
readability levels:

  - viki_*.txt — the "easy" version, from Vikidia (fr.vikidia.org)
  - wiki_*.txt — the "hard" version, from French Wikipedia (fr.wikipedia.org)

Source dataset
--------------
The pairs were randomly sampled from the French portion of WikiReaD
(Wikipedia Readability Dataset):

  Trokhymovych, M., Sen, I., & Gerlach, M. (2024). WikiReaD (Wikipedia
  Readability Dataset). Zenodo. https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.11371932

  Accompanying paper: Trokhymovych, M., Sen, I., & Gerlach, M. (2024).
  An Open Multilingual System for Scoring Readability of Wikipedia.
  Proceedings of the 62nd Annual Meeting of the Association for
  Computational Linguistics (ACL 2024).
  https://aclanthology.org/2024.acl-long.342/

The numeric file IDs (e.g. viki_10164 / wiki_10164) are pair identifiers
from that dataset, not Vikidia/Wikipedia page IDs.

